# Exercise 1

```{r}
for(i in 1:9)
{
    if (i == 9)
    {
        cat("*")
    }

    cat("\n")
}
```

# Exercise 2

```{r}
for(i in 1:10)
{
    cat("*")

    if (i < 10)
    {
        cat("&")
    }
}
```

# Exercise 3

Variable | Start Value | End Value
---- | ---- | ----
dogs | 10 | 15
meatloaf | 0 | -30
bubbles | 12 | -4

